Title: As an admin I can register with valid credentials
As an admin I can reset password with valid credentials
As an admin I can not reset password with empty new password
As an admin I can not reset password with empty invalid password
As an admin I can search admin by id with valid credentials
As an admin I can not search admin by id without login
As a user I can create complaint with valid credentials
As a user I can not create complaint without invalid ID
As a user I can not create complaint without title
As a user I can not create complaint without content
